# Build Performance Rules

## Route Groups
The app has 5 route groups that all compile in one next build:
- (admin) — admin panel
- (book) — player booking portal
- (player) — player PWA
- (staff) — staff dashboard  
- (tv) — TV display
- (courtpay) — CourtPay PWA

## Static Generation
- Never use generateStaticParams in any (book), (player), or (staff) route
- Always add export const dynamic = 'force-dynamic' to all pages under (book)/
- Never add getStaticProps patterns to any customer-facing portal page
- Admin pages can be dynamic too — no page in this app benefits from static generation since all data is venue-scoped and auth-gated

## Dependencies
- Always check if a package already exists in the codebase before installing a new one
- Never install two packages that do the same thing (e.g. two date libraries, two auth libraries)
